{"id": 769, "genre": 1001, "title": "以后咱有无人车了，你觉得可以解放双手干点啥？", "description": "广播再见，我要在车里弄了一个十几吋的屏幕大家一起看片儿！（题图来自：Rami Niemi ）", "record_count": 1614, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071943033EiDf0H7cOMCPJFX.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-31T01:06:03Z", "options": [{"id": 45313, "content": "不用考驾照囖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448990}, {"id": 50689, "content": "打炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475220}, {"id": 45314, "content": "啊啊 痛苦啊 刷钱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449040}, {"id": 45315, "content": "做淘宝什么的都弱爆了，现在流行手机app免费试用，试用了就会有奖励，奖励可通过支付宝或者微信钱包提取，详细了解加qq497839917，仅限苹果手机用户。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 385774}, {"id": 45827, "content": "做科技创新，做出下一个科技", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343002}, {"id": 45316, "content": "想做兼职的加qq497839917，有手机有wifi就可以做任务了，在家或者单位都可以做，轻松赚取零花钱，做的好还可以当主要经济收入呢，仅限苹果手机用户。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 385774}, {"id": 45318, "content": "造小孩\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449119}, {"id": 45319, "content": "补粉什么的弱爆了，吃个粉的时间都有了好么！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393379}, {"id": 45832, "content": "把每天1分钟的早餐时间，放在车里吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422331}, {"id": 46344, "content": "让邻座的她给你好好舒服一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446327}, {"id": 45331, "content": "能涮个火锅吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 45333, "content": "我得看着它 感觉电脑再厉害也不如人脑 还是比较相信自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449305}, {"id": 45334, "content": "自拍", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004613QieTmlg6bAhP2oNR.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449375}, {"id": 45340, "content": "车车都是房车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416023}, {"id": 49700, "content": "sex", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464039}, {"id": 45351, "content": "吃早饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168068}, {"id": 46125, "content": "学习一些对自己有用的知识，将这些碎片化时间充分利用起来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453306}, {"id": 45358, "content": "你还让我说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449659}, {"id": 46383, "content": "出门随便喝，不算酒驾", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454313}, {"id": 45360, "content": "工作学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402880}, {"id": 45365, "content": "挖鼻屎", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116078}, {"id": 45366, "content": "无人驾驶 除了吃饭睡觉 还能有什么呢，啪啪啪也行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348957}, {"id": 45369, "content": "早上中午可以好好解决早饭，有时间可以看看工作安排～晚上可以好好想想回家做什么菜～或者就是简单的补个眠～时间省了下来，干啥都行呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449463}, {"id": 49978, "content": "生个二胎，解放一下天性", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468734}, {"id": 45644, "content": "首先得有辆车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3797}, {"id": 45390, "content": "看好奇心日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 426349}, {"id": 45915, "content": "在睡梦中达成环游世界一圈的梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 452124}, {"id": 46172, "content": "拤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453601}, {"id": 45415, "content": "看好奇心日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392684}, {"id": 45420, "content": "无人车的话，还用考驾照吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450033}, {"id": 45423, "content": "刷手机 鄙视旁边车 一个人从天窗伸出头玩 打炮咬 车内会议 打牌 打麻将 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448587}, {"id": 50294, "content": "_(:з」∠)_那路上就该更堵了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471722}, {"id": 41343, "content": "上班的途中可以光明正大地打盹儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 45439, "content": "放风筝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444996}, {"id": 41344, "content": "以前只能靠堵车那会儿补个粉，现在画眼线都没问题！（戳瞎）", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 41345, "content": "无人房车，在里面开轰趴", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 45441, "content": "喝酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289868}, {"id": 48513, "content": "和宠物狗玩接方向盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462491}, {"id": 41346, "content": "专车司机用上了无人车，应该也是有空掐死那些挑剔的乘客了", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 45444, "content": "既然是无人车 坐上去 (┘⊙ω⊙)┘我选择狗带", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450173}, {"id": 50052, "content": "吃早餐有空了。也不必接孩子上下学了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470279}, {"id": 45446, "content": "戴个VR，至于你想干嘛\n不重要  xxoo", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417375}, {"id": 45452, "content": "先不说解放双手干嘛 那得多堵啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436675}, {"id": 45708, "content": "来来来做无人老司机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451406}, {"id": 45711, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect"